lyrics:
[verse]
Сонечка и Миленочка, like the sun and the moon
Together they shine, bringing joy in tune
Hand in hand, they dance under the silver moonlight
Their love, so pure and bright

[chorus]
Сонечка и Миленочка, a love so true
Forever in each other's arms, they'll stay through
Their hearts connected, a bond that won't sever
A love story that lasts forever
